metadata.name: Hamstroo #1
metadata.description:
Hamstroo Collection is a unique collection of 3000 pieces of 50 characters specially designed for you. A community of people whose dreams have come true or who want to make their dreams come true. Special events for community members, unique tickets, specially designed jewelry. Invitations to exclusive access fashion shows in the Fashion section. Products exclusive to community members. Priority for future roadmaps. Unique digital collectibles that live on the Hamstroo Ethereum blockchain- with which we are always together.

www.hamstroo.com details.
